Le ndoda eneminyaka ewu-38 igwetshwe yinkantolo yaseRichards Bay, ngoMsombuluko. Isigwebo sayo sihlanganisa necala lokudlwengula umngani wendodakazi yakhe le abeyidlengula, owayevakashile. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uCaptain Nqobile Gwala, uthe icala lokudlwengula lavulwa esiteshini samaphoyisa eRichards Bay, idokodo lathunyelwa ophikweni oluphenya izigameko ezithinta udlame lwemindeni, ukuvikelwa kwezingane namacala athinta ucansi, okuyilo olwabopha le ndoda. Lo mdlwenguli wavela enkantolo wadedelwa ngebheyili, ngoMsombuluko utholakale enecala wagwetshwa odilikajele abahlanu. 